            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1702997313185-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the chicken is lightly browned, transfer the <strong>browned</strong> <strong>chicken</strong> to an oven-proof dish and pour over any excess marinade</p><p>Put the dish in the oven for 12-14 min or until cooked through (no pink meat!) and slightly charred – this is your <strong>roasted jerk chicken</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
